ZTE USB Modem CDRUN enabler / disabler

Usage: python ztecdrun.py [port] [enable/disable]

Example to disable CDRUN on /dev/ttyUSB1:

python ztecdrun.py /dev/ttyUSB1 disable


Why would you use this?
Most Telstra NextG USB dongle modems appear in Linux as a CD Drive first. Using this script this behaviour can be disabled and the modem can be used again as a normal USB modem.

